                    <p className="text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-300 font-medium">
                      <strong className="text-white">Personality Check:</strong> Understand their communication style and what makes them tick.
                    </p>
                  </li>
                  <li className="flex gap-4">
                    <div className="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">03</div>
